snippet.title: 3 out of 10, EP 3: "Pivot Like A Champion"
snippet.description: Join the ongoing adventures of developers at the world's worst video game studio as they endure antics both absurd and topical. This week the team settles a question the way only game developers can; with an office wide Battle Royale.
